      "message": "Done. I replaced the one-by-one free helper with span-based freeing: RDMA_TXQ_INVALID_BUF entries are skipped, and each contiguous range of real buffer indices is freed with vlib_buffer_free(). For the non-TSO case, where there are no sentinel WQEBBs, this preserves the fast contiguous free behavior instead of freeing every buffer individually.",
